    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1880-08-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1880-08-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="48"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d48">
                <head>No. 48.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Kasson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Evarts</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Vienna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1880-08-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 7, 1880</date>. (Received August
                        23.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 352.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> In my No. 2931 reported in part the results of
                    the late census of Bosnia-Herzegovina; since then, the Austrian authorities have
                    completed the revision of the enumeration, and the new statement makes some
                    corrections of the former figures, and affords some additional information. The
                    following figures are said to be exact: There are reckoned 43 towns and 1
                    suburb; 31 boroughs and 5,154 villages, with a total of 189,662 houses and
                    1,158,440 native inhabitants; of whom are males 607,789, and females
                    550,651.</p>
                <table cols="2" rows="6">
                    <row>
                        <cell>Religions:</cell>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Mahomedans</cell>
                        <cell role="num">448,613</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Greek Orthodox</cell>
                        <cell role="num">496,761</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Roman Catholics</cell>
                        <cell role="num">209,731</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Israelites</cell>
                        <cell role="num">3,426</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell>Various</cell>
                        <cell role="num">249</cell>
                    </row>
                </table>
                <p>Statistics of wealth taken at the same time show the following results: <table
                        cols="2" rows="9">
                        <row>
                            <cell>Horses</cell>
                            <cell role="num">158,034</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Asses</cell>
                            <cell role="num">2,721</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Mules</cell>
                            <cell role="num">413</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Cattle</cell>
                            <cell role="num">761,312</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Buffaloes</cell>
                            <cell role="num">775</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Sheep</cell>
                            <cell role="num">893,998</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Goats</cell>
                            <cell role="num">522,123</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Hogs</cell>
                            <cell role="num">430,354</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Bee-hives</cell>
                            <cell role="num">111,148</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>No statistics are yet given of the quantity or value of either wild or cultivated
                    land, or of the crops produced.</p>
                <p>I have, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>JOHN A. KASSON.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
